<body>
    <h1>Scrambled Eggs</h1>
    <p>Eggs are one of my favorite foods. Here is a recipe for deliciously rich scrambled eggs.
    </p>
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li> 2 eggs</li>
        <li>1tbs butter</li>
        <li>2tbs cream</li>
    </ul>


    <h2>method<h2>
    <ol>
        <li> Melt butter in a frying pan over medium heat.
        <li> Gently mic the eggs and cream in the bowl.
        <li> Once butter has melted add cream and eggs.
        <li> Using a spatula fold the eggs from the pan to the center every 20 seconds(as if you are making and omelette.)
        <li>When the eggs are still moist remove from the heat(it will continue to cook on the plate until served)</li>

</body>
</html>